What makes the difference

   Customer Success Manager
   The challenge key point for a successful implementation of the digital
   sales assistant solution is a strategic coaching of your sales team.
   This is why we make available a unique contact who will accompany you
   from preparatory stage of the project (Managers training session in
   pilots stores, sharing of best practices…) and all along your project
   (sales animation, challenge implementation, performance analysis,
   reportings, sales team feedbacks, visit in store…).
   Support et maintenance
   An inoperative tablet or a technical issue breaks the quality of
   service you offer to your customers. That’s the reason why we provide a
   high quality technical support able to find the right solution to any
   issue. You’ve got technical issues ? Your sales team have questions
   about the solution ? We’ll do our best to fix the problem by phone, and
   if that does not work, we send you a new setting tablet within 24
   hours.
   Mobile device management
   Another key issue of your project : the management of your device
   fleet. The purpose is to be able to know in real time any info on your
   device fleet (battery level, internet connection, how your sales team
   use the tablet…) and being able to make changes remotely. Then, in one
   click, from the headquarters, you will be able to restrain apps on the
   tablets distributed across the country, send messages to your stores...
